data.description: Location, location! Explore the essence of comfortable living in this remarkable Deltona property awaiting your ownership. Immerse yourself in the charm of this fully remodeled 3-bedroom, two full bathroom home with top-notch upgrades. Revel in the stunning, durable "life proof" vinyl plank flooring, complemented by sleek stainless steel appliances and meticulously refinished lighting fixtures. Let's highlight the best features: REROOF in 2022, a recent water heater, an updated electrical panel with new switches – all from 2022 – and a new 2.5-ton AC system with transferable parts for the next 10 years. Plus, enjoy the freedom of NO HOA fees. The property also boasts an attractive backyard oasis, creating the perfect retreat. Surrounding amenities include Campbell Park, Deltona Youth Soccer Club, Dewey O. Boster Sports Complex, Deltona Landing, and more, all within a 5-minute radius! Don't miss out – schedule your appointment now and seize the opportunity to call this beautiful property your home!!
